                        <div class="page-title">
    <h1>Library </h1>
    <a href="#" class="print-page" id="print-page"><img src="/img/print-btn.png" alt="print-icon"  /></a></div>

<p><strong><img src="/abs-file-image-show/id/ckVxyf4CPXvpEqOH9gqs_w" alt="library books" width="725" height="192" /></strong></p>
<p><strong>Vision Statement</strong><br />Your library, your destination to discover &amp; uncover life&rsquo;s possibilities</p>
<p><strong>Our Mission</strong><br />To be a welcoming upbeat community hub, enhancing the quality of life for all, empowering everyone to reach their potential through access to resources &amp; activities for relaxation &amp; lifelong learning.</p>
<p><strong>What we do</strong><br />The public library is open to everyone, regardless of your background, education, or place of residence. We provide a place in the heart of Hanover, to spend time, meet people, relax or learn.</p>
<p>Our facility provides tourist information, newspapers, magazines, computers, Internet access, local history, reference resources, movies, and audio and print books for all ages. We also offer programming and activities for children, and a venue for social groups of writers, knitters, and board game players.</p>
<p><strong>Please&nbsp;visit the&nbsp;</strong><a href="http://hanoverlibrary.ca/" target="_blank"><strong>Hanover Public Library</strong></a><strong> website for further information.</strong></p>
<hr />
<p>&nbsp;</p>
